Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本字幕由喵萌奶茶屋制作 仅供交流试看之用 请勿用于商业用途\N\N翻译：Nemeton　后期：MIR　繁化：错党
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.36,0:00:05.46,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,德勒韦斯大人怎么会在这？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:07.14,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,一会再说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:08.89,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,火焰风暴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:14.35,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,我来开路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.36,0:00:16.06,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:05.05,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,好 长势不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:07.85,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们开始下一个阶段吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:10.87,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,可以用这片地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.17,0:02:14.45,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 领主大人已经同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:16.28,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,那就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:16.92,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:33.13,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个就是圣女之术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.57,0:02:35.55,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:37.79,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个就是圣女之术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:40.15,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经可以自由使用了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.44,0:02:43.19,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,不过你为什么要在这种地方使用…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:45.89,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,更重要的是为什么不在我面前使用？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:48.15,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,欺负我吗？还是说故意使坏？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.95,0:02:49.95,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.07,0:02:54.25,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,是我想要练习一下魔法 所以她带我来了这边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:56.17,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:03:00.67,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,这边才刚刚准备好 还什么都没有种
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:04.30,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,圣女之术也不会对田地有危害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:05.61,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:11.83,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,不过虽说没有危害 可对土地说不定有影响
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:12.45,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:16.61,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,能感觉到奇特的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:19.24,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,能判断出有什么样的影响吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:21.77,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,不确定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:24.63,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,要么魔力会滞留在土地中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.81,0:03:27.98,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,要么就是矿物会被附魔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.98,0:03:30.23,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,两种情况都有可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.63,0:03:33.49,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,现在也就是假设阶段而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:37.00,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,要仔细验证一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:38.24,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:41.66,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,这两人聊得怪开心…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:44.96,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们开始下一步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:45.94,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:47.52,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:54.95,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.68,0:03:55.97,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:03:57.17,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.20,0:04:00.36,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,诶?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:12.16,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,看来圣女之术会消耗大量的魔力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:14.69,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:16.88,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 如你所见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:19.82,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是让我连续用了好几次…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:22.94,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,反复练习才能掌握好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.41,0:04:28.40,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,以后还得多加练习 提升发动魔法的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:31.38,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,诶？还…还要更快吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:33.79,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,那是不是有点…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:38.04,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,发动魔法之前我需要不少准备的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:39.52,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,准备？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:43.86,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来发动的条件是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.33,0:04:46.78,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,诶？那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:48.13,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:51.02,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,不好说出来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:04:55.11,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗 那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:57.04,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,诶？这就算了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:04:59.11,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,难道你愿意说出来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:01.06,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:04.21,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:07.62,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,圣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:09.12,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,霍克大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:12.67,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,打搅了 我听说你在这边…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:16.44,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意 你有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:19.10,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,讨伐队伍重新编排好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:20.80,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:23.08,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,圣也一起确认一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:27.70,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,我这边没什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:29.08,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:32.28,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,史莱姆吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:34.56,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,有点等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:50.10,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,圣小姐 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:52.11,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,爱良 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:54.35,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,我们好像是一队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:58.05,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 爱良也要参与进攻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:06:00.91,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,估计是要看情况…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:03.42,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我基本上是负责治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:07.40,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,因为前辈说团长大概不会参与治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:09.12,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:12.89,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 圣大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:15.32,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:16.69,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,哟！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:19.29,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,莱昂先生也和我们一队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.51,0:06:21.00,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:22.68,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 圣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:25.48,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,圣大人 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:27.13,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:29.70,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是灰烬恶魔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.67,0:06:31.51,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:34.14,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,某次大规模讨伐任务中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:37.81,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,他将怪物连同周围的一切都燃烧殆尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:39.93,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就有了这么个外号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:43.49,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,希望他能控制住自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:44.72,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:48.35,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,希望这次任务的森林没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:50.73,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:54.82,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,得提前拜托他别引燃森林…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:08.07,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,冰矛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:12.66,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,范围守护
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:15.01,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,火矛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:18.59,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:23.28,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,姑娘 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.66,0:07:24.10,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:26.93,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,圣女大人 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:28.43,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.89,0:07:30.69,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,怪物的数量增多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:33.39,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,史莱姆的数量也变多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.13,0:07:36.38,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定离那沼泽不远了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:37.93,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,德勒韦斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:41.71,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 爱护森林是吧 我没忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:09.35,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,怪物出现了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:10.38,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,迎敌！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:11.25,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,数量太多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:12.43,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,保持警戒！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:18.56,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,火矛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.95,0:08:24.16,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,保持阵型！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:26.25,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:28.89,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,水墙！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:32.22,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,冰箭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:38.24,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,冰墙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:41.21,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,地刺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:48.64,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:50.70,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:53.41,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,圣！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:05.23,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,霍克大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:07.91,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,还不是时候 火矛！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:15.26,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:17.07,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,没事 圣大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.33,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:19.47,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.01,0:09:22.66,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.30,0:09:26.73,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:27.72,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:31.93,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,只是圣女之术消耗的魔力过多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:34.44,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,在找到沼泽之前希望你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:44.92,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:11.95,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,圣大人 从这个位置可以净化到黑色沼泽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:15.92,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,能…能不能靠近一些…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:18.96,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我想想办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:26.59,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样我们现在也无法撤退 只有前进了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:36.71,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,准备上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.67,0:10:39.99,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,火矛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:44.05,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,全员冲锋！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:47.14,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,电团
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:10:58.20,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,圣大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:00.50,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,旋风
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:03.93,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,快！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:05.18,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:27.30,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,团长！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:29.44,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,霍克大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:33.31,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,我们来对付史莱姆 圣大人专注发动魔法…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:38.04,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,圣大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:40.13,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,圣！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:53.04,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,业火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:10.49,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,圣大人 趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:12.43,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,火矛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:23.69,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧时间 必须抓紧时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:44.37,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:49.26,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,没事 只是在发呆…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:53.23,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 今天很不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:56.98,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,你也累了吧 早些休息比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:14:00.33,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢团长…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:05.88,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,圣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:10.50,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 那我就先休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:12.49,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,我送你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:14.31,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:15.46,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:24.88,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:28.64,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,不必在意 那你好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.02,0:14:30.78,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:32.16,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:52.05,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是有什么心事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:59.77,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 再要求更多就有些任性了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:05.73,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我还是无法就这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.21,0:15:13.53,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,圣 我是王国的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:16.87,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,我的剑就是王的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:20.34,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,可如果可能的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:23.39,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望成为守护你的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.49,0:15:28.15,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,能否让我实现你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:20.67,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:24.67,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个 那什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:30.12,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,要专心 专心…专心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:33.62,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:34.93,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:39.85,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,不是…你一直盯着我 我不好集中注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:42.76,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 你请便 不用在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:50.19,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以做到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.18,0:17:06.29,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:14.31,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:44.36,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,愿森林恢复生机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:15.04,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.81,0:18:18.46,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:25.17,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,这是…克劳斯纳的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.73,0:18:44.27,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,圣？圣！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:45.45,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,圣小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:45.95,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,圣大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:46.46,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,圣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:59.39,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:01.77,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么会这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.77,0:19:05.52,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,你是累坏了吧 突然就倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.90,0:19:09.55,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我真的没事了 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.55,0:19:11.59,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你让我们担心的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.94,0:19:26.32,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.09,0:19:34.49,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,我想自己走…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:37.58,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:57.93,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,那至少能让我陪伴着你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:00.74,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:12.90,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:16.60,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,没有 我才是得到了不少帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:20.89,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,你不在了 药水制作又不容易了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.93,0:20:22.54,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,不至于…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:27.71,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么不至于 只有你能制作那么多药水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:34.21,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,不过正如领主大人所说 你就是我们的希望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:35.17,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:37.76,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,哟！准备回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:38.77,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.28,0:20:40.27,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.82,0:20:42.17,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,莱昂先生也多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:46.18,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 王都待烦了随时可以来这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:51.12,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢 交给你还不如让她来我这
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:53.16,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,圣 该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:54.32,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.11,0:20:57.22,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们的帮助和照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:20:59.65,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎再来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.71,0:21:07.70,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,圣女的魔力还真是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.21,0:21:10.19,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然连森林都再生了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:11.73,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:15.27,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,不过她的厉害之处不只是魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:19.38,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,其实我们都拥有那样的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:22.72,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？老太你一把年纪 人傻了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:24.07,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.07,0:21:25.78,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,不是什么复杂的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:28.72,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,圣女的魔力…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:31.22,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,就是爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.30,0:23:09.12,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,还是自己家最舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.06,0:23:16.58,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,过不了多久又会有新的讨伐任务吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.30,0:23:19.21,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,又要麻烦圣了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.76,0:23:20.84,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.72,0:23:22.23,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.30,0:23:26.55,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 霍克大人不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.15,0:23:29.51,Dial-CHS,,0000,0000,0000,,圣女的魔力…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:58.81,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,「返回」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:04.01,Scr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\pos(262,513)}圣女魔力无所不能
