Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.07,0:19:59.44,OP2-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur2\fad(480,480)\bord1\fscx90\fscy90}Your tenderness
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.93,0:20:06.52,OP2-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur2\fad(480,2000)\bord1\fscx90\fscy90}I want to tell you everything about my day
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.01,0:20:11.06,OP2-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur2\fad(480,480)\bord1\fscx90\fscy90}Especially when something good has happened
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.06,0:20:19.58,OP2-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur2\fad(480,480)\bord1\fscx90\fscy90}And if {\alpha&HFF&\t(4000,4400,\alpha&H00&)}I ever saw you down I’ll hold you tight
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.36,0:20:22.54,OP2-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur2\fad(480,480)\bord1\fscx90\fscy90}I won’t ever let go
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.51,0:20:47.12,OP2-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur2\fad(480,480)\bord1\fscx90\fscy90}Because of you the sadness all disappears
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.19,0:20:51.49,OP2-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur2\fad(480,480)\bord1\fscx90\fscy90}The nights don’t seem so scary anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.86,0:20:59.65,OP2-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur2\fad(480,480)\bord1\fscx90\fscy90}And now in gracefulness my flower starts to bloom
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.20,0:21:05.80,OP2-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur2\fad(480,480)\bord1\fscx90\fscy90}My heart skips a beat
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.80,0:21:11.73,OP2-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur2\fad(480,480)\bord1\fscx90\fscy90}But it’s so hard to show what I’m feeling
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.38,0:21:20.66,OP2-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur2\fad(480,480)\bord1\fscx90\fscy90}I just can’t help it somehow I say all the wrong words
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.85,0:21:23.09,OP2-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur2\fad(480,480)\bord1\fscx90\fscy90}It’s funny, I know…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.67,0:21:44.66,OP2-JP,,0560,0000,0020,,{\fad(480,480)\fscx90\fscy90}What is precious to you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.92,0:21:47.41,OP2-JP,,0560,0000,0020,,{\fad(480,480)\fscx90\fscy90}You are always there in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:51.48,OP2-JP,,0560,0000,0020,,{\fad(480,480)\fscx70\fscy70}Make me brave and make me stronger, it’s true
